### GET all meals (with meal_items, foods, and measures)
GET http://localhost:3000/meals
Accept: application/json

###

### GET a single meal
GET http://localhost:3000/meals/1
Accept: application/json

###

### CREATE a meal with nested meal_items
POST http://localhost:3000/meals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "meal": {
    "name": "Breakfast",
    "meal_items_attributes": [
      { "food_id": 1, "measure_id": 3, "quantity": 2 },
      { "food_id": 2, "measure_id": 5, "quantity": 1.5 }
    ]
  }
}

###

### UPDATE a meal + its meal_items
PATCH http://localhost:3000/meals/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "meal": {
    "name": "Updated Breakfast",
    "meal_items_attributes": [
      { "id": 5, "quantity": 3 },          # update existing item
      { "food_id": 3, "measure_id": 2, "quantity": 1 }  # add new item
    ]
  }
}

###

### DELETE a meal
DELETE http://localhost:3000/meals/1
